Instalation.

Simple. Really. 

1. Put the Skymap directory somwhere you want your matlab-files, like ~/matlab
2. Add the Skymap directory to your matlab-path.
4. Set execute permission for /stars/getsp
4.1 If you are on a system whithout the c-shell you have to install
    that in order to get the stellar spectra out of the Pulkovo
    spectrophotometric catalog. 
4.2 If you work in an operating-system that doesn't have a /tmp
    directory for temporary files then you will have to modify the
    paths to the test1.qWe and stasr12.qwe in the files getspec.m,
    makespec.m, guigetspec.m and plotspec.m
5. Done
